Installation from egg
---------------------

wget http://www.nickblundell.org.uk/ez_setup.py
sudo python ez_setup.py
sudo easy_install -f http://www.nickblundell.org.uk/packages smartbox
sudo smartbox install

When smartbox is installed and configured, open the server's address in a browser and log in with default user/password: Administrator/smartbox
